Class BankTellerController

java.lang.Object
src.main.java.com.example.project3.BankTellerController
public class BankTellerController extends Object
This class serves as the link between the UI and our code from project 2. It allows us to interact with all of the code of the previous project through buttons and text fields in the UI.
